{"about_the_game":"Never Give Up is a masocore, tough-as-nails groundhog day platformer where levels respawn with more obstacles and rooms until you survive the set or Give Up.<br><strong><br><i>&quot;This Game Looks Too Hard&quot;</i></strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/609420/extras/giveup-shorter.gif?t=1726581244\" /><br><br>If you're on the fence about whether this game is for you, here are some things you might not know about Never Give Up.<br><br>     \u2022 <strong>Easy Mode</strong> - Play with checkpoints, we're not judging.<br>     \u2022 <strong>Infinite Jump Mode</strong> - Yes, you read that correctly - go nuts, float above it all.<br>     \u2022 <strong>Give Up Button</strong> - Skip to the next level, return when you've cooled off, or don't.<br><br>It's true Never Give Up was designed to be very difficult, but it was also designed to allow players some control over just <i>how</i> difficult.  Everyone should have a chance to never give up.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/609420/extras/blue_steam_600_75q.gif?t=1726581244\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/609420/extras/header_features_(1).png?t=1726581244\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 6 unique worlds and boss battles<br></li><li> 30 level sets totaling over 150 levels<br></li><li> 155 collectible coins placed in tantalizing, precarious positions<br></li><li> 30 secret objects hidden throughout the game<br></li><li> 21 unlockable outfits (gotta look cute for your date with a buzzsaw)<br></li><li> 1 Egoraptor taunting you throughout the entire game<br></li><li> Leaderboards, split timers, speedrunning tools, and more<br><br>We've also included accessibility features such as button remapping, contrast sliders, and animation/screenshake toggles for folks with sensitivities to these sorts of things.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/609420/extras/butt-gif_(1).png?t=1726581244\" /></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Ghostbuster!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/609420/5bf1c4bccc4686c3a4615166ebcedd8d3eaf0471.jpg"},{"name":"Searching. Seek & destroy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/609420/344927398518692e9231e3c4acd09394462f5e9a.jpg"},{"name":"I'll be back, and I am","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/609420/13868bb8e735aa905a8b0d583f557e142ffb7db1.jpg"},{"name":"Original gangsta","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/609420/b9ec33ef9e05f0670d394f4aeb738103105b80e0.jpg"},{"name":"Fashionista","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/609420/1c28ad9dafb78214f20a3048b307abfbf2fb9345.jpg"},{"name":"What sorcery is this?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/609420/adc756a298bd1d96fd053fef9bb4b1421fca9cc0.jpg"},{"name":"There is no escape","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/609420/53e37d92fdd5de7daed499999c1977b6740c12f1.jpg"},{"name":"You shot first","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/609420/5fae2bcde26ad82da428e8a66efcce3a52b2cdbd.jpg"},{"name":"You're going the wrong way","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/609420/8c9ec66f70588224728ed47d5d2d4f741fba6cf2.jpg"},{"name":"A checkpoint ain't one","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/609420/a5b32d422c1c988d7c6d1cc97e8b0f9e08f2dbbb.jpg"}],"total":49},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/609420/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1726581244","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstati